{"word":"κῶας","slug":"κῶας","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n61180\" key=\"kw=as\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">κῶας</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">τό</gen>, in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hom.</author> </bibl> nom. acc. sg. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κῶας</foreign>; pl. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κώεα</foreign>, dat. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κώεσι</foreign>; later <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"var\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ contr.\">contr.</a></gram> </gramGrp> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κῶς</foreign> (q.v.):—<sense id=\"n61180.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">fleece</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">στόρεσαν λέχος, . . κώεά τε ῥῆγός τε</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:9:661\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9.661</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:23:180\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">23.180</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἀδέψητον βοέην στόρεσ᾽, αὐτὰρ ὕπερθε κώεα πόλλ᾽ ὀΐων</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:20:3\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">20.3</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:142\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">142</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">χεῦεν ὕπο χλωρὰς ῥῶπας καὶ κῶας ὕπερθεν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:16:47\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">16.47</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">φέρε δὴ δίφρον καὶ κῶας ἐπ᾽ αὐτοῦ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:19:97\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">19.97</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἵδρυσεν παρὰ δαιτί κώεσιν ἐν μαλακοῖσι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:3:38\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.38</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:17:32\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">17.32</biblScope> </bibl>; of the <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">Golden Fleece</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">κ. αἰγλᾶεν χρυσέῳ θυσάνῳ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0033.tlg002.perseus-grc1:4:231\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pi.\">Pi.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ P.\">P.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.231</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἔπλεον ἐπὶ τὸ κ. ἐς Αἶαν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0016.tlg001.perseus-grc1:7:193\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.193</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">μέγα κ.</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0255.tlg001:11:1\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Mimn.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">11.1</b